  <brief_title>Falls and Cardiovascular Events in Pacemaker Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Falls and Cardiovascular Events in Elderly Patients With Sinus Node Disease Treated With a MVPTM Pacemaker According to the ESC 2007 Guidelines</official_title>
