  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Sinus Node Disease (SND) treated with a pacemaker with MVP (TM) mode according to ESC
             2007 guidelines (SND as primary indication for pacemaker implant, implant within past
             two weeks)

          -  Geographic stability and availability for follow-up at the study center for the length
             of the study

          -  Willingness and Ability to sign Informed Consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age less than 50 years

          -  Impaired cognitive function (such as Alzheimer's disease)

          -  permanent AV Block II and III

          -  Persistent atrial fibrillation

          -  Life expectancy less than two years

          -  Enrollment or intended participation in another clinical trial during the course of
             this study

          -  Subject is pregnant or breastfeeding
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
